Revision history for Perinci-Sub-Property-retry

0.07     2014-03-07 (SHARYANTO)

         - Adjust to Perinci::Sub::Wrapper 0.51+.

         - Pass special argument '-retries' to function, so function can be
           aware about retries.

         [INCOMPATIBLE CHANGES]

         - Rename result metadata property 'wrap_retries' to 'retries'.


0.06     2012-12-21 (SHARYANTO)

         - No functional changes. Use Perinci::Sub::PropertyUtil.


0.05     2012-11-27 (SHARYANTO)

         - No functional changes. Correct namespace.


0.04     2012-08-09 (SHARYANTO)

         - No functional changes. Correct casing in name:
           Perinci::Sub::{p,P}roperty::


0.03     2012-07-31 (SHARYANTO)

         - No functional changes. Update to wrapping protocol version 2.


0.02     2012-07-31 (SHARYANTO)

         [ENHANCEMENTS]

         - Add params: {,non_}fatal_{statuses,messages}.


0.01     2012-02-13 (SHARYANTO)

         - First release.
